{"tid":719141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪一擊既血肉長城！","createTime":"2018-06-27T08:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T08:05:08.000Z","uid":116054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f3238e4b78c9cb5e53a343fb1bbb28815ce8ac","tid":719141,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"【今日跌啲咩】近4億元血肉長城一下打爆！騰訊跌穿380元<br />\nA股一度跌穿2800，港股不能倖免，大市午後氣氛轉差，跌逾400點，股王騰訊（700）獲大批散戶撈底，於380元價位共錄近1,700牌，共100萬股的買盤，平均每牌588股，涉資3.8億元，惟買盤數分鐘內即被消化，騰訊現跌1.78%，報379.2元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180627/58369858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58369858&d=e7G7iAUUHYrUboZIHzTv4f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=309ff3a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180627%2F58369858&h=2d22f3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180627/58369858</a>"}]}